DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-21T04:30:00&endDate=2026-03-23T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Saturday 21 and Sunday 22 March\, no service between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Use VICTORIA LINE connections between Central London and Seven Sisters / Walthamstow Central. GREATER ANGLIA and STANSTED EXPRESS trains will not call at Liverpool Street\, Hackney Downs and Seven Sisters and start and terminate at Stratford. Replacement buses operate. If travelling to the Tottenham Hotspur vs Nottingham Forest match on Sunday\, please use VICTORIA LINE services to Seven Sisters or Tottenham Hale\, or GREATER ANGLIA services at Northumberland Park.
